U.K. to Support Rockhopper in Falkland Exploration, Times Says

-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 
2011-09-18T09:10:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/u-k-to-support-rockhopper-in-falkland-exploration-times-says.html
The U.K.  Foreign Office  will
support  Rockhopper Exploration Plc (RKH) ’s oilfield development off
the Falkland Islands, the Sunday Times  reported , citing the
government department.  Officials plan to meet Rockhopper investors to assure them
of the government’s commitment to defend the sovereignty of the
overseas territory from possible claims from Argentine, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduard Gismatullin in London at 
 egismatullin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  